  linesWarn:
  - Step over here. Routine check.
  - License and ID, please.
  - I'm going to need you to stop right there.
  linesDemandBribe:
  - Are you... are you trying to bribe an officer?
  - I don't take money. You should know better than this.
  linesAcceptBribe:
  - I'll let it go this time. Don't make me regret it.
  linesRejectBribe:
  - Absolutely not. Keep your money.
  - That is a criminal offense, son.
  - Put that away before I add charges.
  linesArrest:
  - You have the right to remain silent.
  - Don't make this harder than it has to be.
  - By the book. Every time.
  linesAttack:
  - Resisting arrest! Do not run!
  - Stop or I will use force!
